node.text:
GIVEAWAY ALERT
 
We have partnered with @diveblu3 to co-host a very exciting giveaway! One lucky winner will receive a FREE NEMO UNIT.
 
How to enter:
LIKE this post
FOLLOW @pureflorida & @diveblu3
TAG your friends (more tags = more entries)
SHARE this post in your story & tag @pureflorida & @diveblu3 for a bonus entry
Contest ends on 8/26 at 11:59PM EST. You must be 18+ and reside in the U.S. to enter.
 
Good luck!
 
-
Nemo is a tankless, compact dive system that supports 1 diver up to 10 feet. Click the link in the bio for more info.
